<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef7e0e81-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s100802"><num value="100802">§ 100802.</num><heading> Interpretation and education authority</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall ensure that management of System units and related areas is enhanced by the availability and use of a broad program of the highest quality interpretation and education.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idef7e0e82-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/114/289/tIII/s301/a">Pub. L. 114–289, title III, § 301(a)</ref>, <date date="2016-12-16">Dec. 16, 2016</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/130/1487">130 Stat. 1487</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
